{"tid":1380674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推上熱門]開始迷惘嘅你入黎睇","createTime":"2019-07-29T05:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T07:00:20.000Z","uid":102535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"248454ce94c837a829099658fce2d5b5b869d215","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:28:40.000Z","msg":"依幾日聽得最多嘅問題係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解唔走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解要守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要守邊度 守到幾時呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實有時真係會無7月1嗰日咁有明確嘅地點需要攻/包圍<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>既然唔需要攻 點解唔轉換心態係守?</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「只要中後排未走哂，前線都唔會走」</strong></span><br />\n中後排嘅手足就係前線要守護嘅嘢<br />\n前線 其實同時係我地最堅固嘅後方<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊個趨勢 警方係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔會</span></strong>比不反對通知書<br />\n前線可以係路線中間揀定個易守難攻嘅位築起一道防線<br />\n防線預留位置比遊行人士通過<br />\n遊行人士就和理非<br />\n到警察趕嘅就慢慢退返防線<br />\n可以返起點走又或者Backup前線<br />\n等遊行群眾可以安全撤離<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解唔走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">因為中後排未走晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解要守呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">要保護和理非手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要守邊度 守到幾時呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我地要堅守依一條防線 直至手足們安全撤離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n優點有三<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 勇武 和理非分工清晰 合作難度低 減低互屌分化機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n勇武定位就係直面警察，比和理非可以安全撤離<br />\n和理非負責嗌口號，傳遞訊息比嗰區嘅人知道<br />\n唔好忘記運動一開始嘅成功係因為勇武同和理非嘅合作<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2. 前線可以保留體力，更長時間築起防線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n勇武唔洗參與全個遊行，節省體力<br />\n遊行前預先決定防線位置，到場直接開始建立防線<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 和理非遊行被警察驅趕，加強雞蛋高牆嘅對比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n幾次警察嘅記者會都講話係示威者使用暴力在先，警察逼不得已先採取最低武力，已經非常克制<br />\n我地就利用和理非，完全0威脅，警察一武力驅趕就可以撕破佢嘅假面具<br />\n<br />\n你可能會問: <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你咁樣有撚用咩，依家係要對抗中共政權<br />\n梗係攻佢中聯辦，包圍警總啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我絕對贊成呀，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只要做得到</span></strong><br />\n問題係警察佈重防，佢地最想最開心見到係咩?<br />\n就係你地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自投羅莽</span></span></strong>呀!!!<br />\n警察:<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">陣場戰唔係唔得<br />\n但係要揀個合格嘅陣地</span><br />\n難聽啲講句 你依家個陣地係Set係對家個陷阱到<br />\n附近一堆天橋 制高點比對家拎晒<br />\n就算武力對等都嬴唔到啦下話<br />\n<br />\n由攻變守唔等於我地唔能夠Make Noise<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其實行動已經係宣傳嘅一種</strong></span><br />\n十八區遊行光復行動<br />\n個人認為目的或者效果有以下兩點<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 喚醒該區居民</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n居民親身體驗警察如何對待示威者 勝過我地講千言萬語<br />\n例如沙田新城市行街嘅市民，元朗落樓比警察兇嘅居民，今日上環麥當勞食催淚彈嘅家庭<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 為抗爭運動保溫</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人係善忘 每個禮拜提醒佢地係必需<br />\n亦都向政府同警察施加壓力<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武嘅手足<br />\n除咗係最強嘅矛<br />\n亦都可以係最強嘅盾</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86eda3a48d38e5839230c04a707e42f11cfc5bda","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"429a0ce9147111bc1e592b0f9bfcfe965812599b","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:32:08.000Z","msg":"依個只係個大方向<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地絕對可以係細節入手</span></strong><br />\n例如利用現有嘅哨兵，或者類似糾察嘅隊伍<br />\n散佈遊行路線<br />\n指示和理非方向同帶領嗌口號<br />\n強烈建議依部分人要有大聲公同行動力高<br />\n同時被警察趕時要負起疏散嘅責任"},{"pid":"5a803e89d6d6a3950ed26cf54f8428debacae92a","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2a0899bd8b7234da1b63aea3ca8a637f953efb1","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:34:45.000Z","msg":"7月30 0730港鐵不合作運動<br />\n8月2晚上公務員集會<br />\n8月5 全港大罷工!!!"},{"pid":"58e8d93104139b99eadd4e438b84ddd7f06039a2","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:36:04.000Z","msg":"7月30 0730港鐵不合作運動<br />\n8月2晚上公務員集會<br />\n8月5 全港大罷工!!!"},{"pid":"9e3fa395174a6d8e0bc7d3958d72c92caaffdc3a","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:39:41.000Z","msg":"7月30 0730港鐵不合作運動<br />\n8月2晚上公務員集會<br />\n8月5 全港大罷工!!!"},{"pid":"e9187fea4b0cad1622844a4b85b4434e2a6e3314","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:40:50.000Z","msg":"推到有人睇"},{"pid":"52cfa40db42dbb697546b8124ef19931a4548354","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"推到有人睇"},{"pid":"87a6d2fde253e02a6ca6209c9e57a83109cb56e9","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:45:52.000Z","msg":"依篇都好有用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378522/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378522/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ccdca6ad0af1d2448c7804087b8c8f81cde7aa10","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:47:02.000Z","msg":"仲有依篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1380271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1380271/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"df8676c5026a9280e0cbfaf8789d4c5b98119ba4","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"e315f70a56b1a836749916020b44d0dc69234474","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82e3debd67657c15c0f5c0ea1382cdf4fc70fd00","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:58:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bc13c0bf629ab1709ee8b1acbbe6ebbdcdbc8e8","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e58c26c00b3dab8a1ddb41a0c4fce9b09b918c9","tid":1380674,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"推"}]}